reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 8, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I bought this for 2 reasons. I wanted a durable fast charging type c, and I wanted it to be visible at night, without a glare.This cable is everything I wanted. It works well and is quite durable. You can tell by it's solid feel that it much more than your standard replacement cable.I use it primarily for my phone, but have also used it to charge my tablet and flashlights.I recommend this cable!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 9, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars An overall great cable.
reviews.reviewText: Even if it didn't have the gentle, multicolored glow, it's still great. Very sturdy flat cable; both port ends seem to have solid reinforcement. It's worked well for both charging and data transfer. I just wish I could get a 3ft version, as that would work well with my charging setup.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 27, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This is a really good charger and looks really neat lit up. The only complaint is it does not completely light up all the way near the top of it it gets a little dim

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 21, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Quality cable, fast charging.
reviews.reviewText: Good quality cable, supports fast charging, LED lighted to show when it is charging. Not too bright that it would affect a dark room while sleeping, but bright enough to know it is working.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Worked for a few mins
reviews.reviewText: Worked for a few mins and just stopped. I did call and get a replacement but the replacement charges so slow. I had it on the charger for about 30 mins and it only went up 2%. It's very pretty but not a fast charger at all and easily breaks.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 24, 2023
Reviewed in the United States on April 21, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars The light isn’t constant.
reviews.reviewText: So for example I’ll have it plugged into my Xbox one and the only time the light will come on is when my controller vibrates, I don’t expect it to stay on when my Xbox is off but I was kinda hoping it would stay on when I’m playing a game. Plus I’ve noticed the light travels faster when it’s plugged into other things like when I use it for a charger on a phone, I figured it’d help me find whatever it’s plugged into when it’s dark but the light doesn’t stay on.

reviews.reviewText: Charges my phones colors are bright , no issues
